title: Liquid Sky  DVDRip.avi
description:
Annie Carlisle wrote the film, and plays dual roles as a girl and boy! It's about two girls living in Manhattan, New York City, one who deals heroin, and an alien.  It's about the club where they hang out, at home, the bodies of dead people. 

Aliens came to this world in search of a chemical that bonds with opium receptors and occurs during orgasm, and found something better: Liquid Sky / heroin (also called scag, smack, or di-acetyl monphine.) 
Have fun...and don't forget to seeeeeed!  
Thanx,
D.J.Tone of the East Village.
